  <div class= "bloc-plan-on">
    <h3 class="title-planon">Plan On</h3>
    <div class="text-planon mt-5">
      <p>
      Plano On is an application, created in 2022, by web developers Yasmin Crisostomo, Gabriel Alvino and Pedro Costa. The study system was created with the purpose of providing an agile and efficient study method that provides success in exams.
      </p>

      <p>
      Focused on a study oriented for Public Exams, Enem and OAB, the app adopts the Wheel of Life as the principal study methodology, we believe that studying should be healthy and integrated with other parts of life.

      <p>
      In this sense, Plan On differs from other applications because it introduces the possibility to conciliate studies, professional life and personal life. In this way, the student with the Wheel of Life, an optimized study plan, a schedule of classes for the day, and a timer, quickly obtains the best results.
      </p>

      <p>
      We at Plan On are happy to contribute to your approval and hope you use our instruments to build a happy and healthy life.
      </p>

    </div>
